quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  30,20,"No mu bimenyetso bye (Allah), ni uko yabaremye abakomoye mu gitaka, none dore muri abantu bakwirakwiye ku isi"
  30,21,"No mu bimenyetso bye ni uko yabaremeye abagore ababakomoyemo (Hawa yakomotse mu rubavu rwa Adamu), kugira ngo mubabonemo ituze, anashyira urukundo n’impuhwe hagati yanyu. Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bantu batekereza"
  30,22,No mu bimenyetso bye (harimo) iremwa ry’ibirere n’isi no gutandukana kw’indimi zanyu ndetse n’amabara y’uruhu rwanyu. Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bantu bafite ubumenyi
  30,23,"No mu bimenyetso bye ni ugusinzira kwanyu nijoro no ku manywa, no gushakisha ingabire ze kwanyu (ku manywa). Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bantu bumva"
  30,24,"No mu bimenyetso bye ni uko abereka imirabyo mukagira ubwoba (bw’inkuba) n’icyizere (cyo kubona imvura), akanamanura amazi mu kirere, akayahesha isi ubuzima nyuma yo gupfa kwayo (gukakara). Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bantu bafite ubwenge"
  30,25,"No mu bimenyetso bye ni uko ikirere n’isi biriho ku bw’itegeko rye. Hanyuma nabahamagara umuhamagaro umwe (w’izuka), icyo gihe muzasohoka mu mva zanyu"
  30,26,Kandi ibiri mu birere no ku isi ni ibye. Byose bimwibombarikaho
  30,27,"Ni We urema ibiremwa bitari biriho akazanabigarura (nyuma yo gupfa); kandi ibyo biroroshye kuri We. Anafite ibisingizo by’ikirenga mu birere no ku isi. Kandi ni Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"